whereas.text:
Whereas on April 15, 2013, innocent civilians were
			 maliciously victimized by Improvised Explosive Devices (IEDs) in a terrorist
			 attack in Boston, Massachusetts;

Whereas IED attacks are the leading cause of casualties
			 for American servicemembers and are anticipated to remain the leading cause of
			 such casualties for the foreseeable future;

Whereas reducing the use of IEDs and neutralizing the
			 networks that produce them requires a holistic approach to identify and
			 eliminate the root causes that allow such networks to form and survive;
